title: Ordinary±
sinopse:
Two assassins met - Imari Matoba, Yayoi Kawaguchi one lost his master and they part.

-   "We'll help each other out if we're in trouble."
-   I have no intention of needing the help of an assassin.
    What does Fate have store for them in the future?
    Will they meet again? As enemies or allies?

(Source: MU)
